title: I AM ATHLETE | ROBBIE ANDERSON: “I Keep a Chip on My Shoulder Because Nothing will Be Handed To Me”
description:
SUBSCRIBE ➡️ https://www.youtube.com/c/IAMATHLETE?sub_confirmation=1
WATCH MORE ➡️ https://www.youtube.com/c/IAMATHLETE

Carolina Panthers wide receiver Robbie Anderson joins Brandon Marshall, Pacman Jones, Shady McCoy and D.J. Williams in episode 42 of I Am Athlete. Watch as Robby discusses  his frustrations last season on field and how his growth allowed him continue to battle and overcome the politics of football.
